 #:books.book{:description             ". . . the great feature of the book is that anyone can read it without excessive head scratching . . . You'll find plenty here to keep you occupied, amused, and informed. Buy, dip in, wallow. -IAN STEWART, NEW SCIENTIST \" . . . a delightful look at numbers and their roles in everything from language to flowers to the imagination\". -SCIENCE NEWS \" . . . a fun and fascinating tour of numerical topics and concepts. It will have readers contemplating ideas they might never have thought were understandable or even possible\". -WISCONSIN BOOKWATCH \"This popularization of number theory looks like another classic\". -LIBRARY JOURNAL",
